<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/study-finds-long-term-health-benefits-from-bariatric-surgery-and-liver-transplant/">Study finds long-term health benefits from bariatric surgery and liver transplant</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
